videos.description: Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. finds the loose ball near the basket and throws down a crowd-pleasing two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Lual-Acuil in right place at right time for emphatic dunk

videos.description: Justin Gray tracks down Justin Lindsey's fast-break dunk attempt and rejects it off the backboard.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Gray gets huge chase-down block

videos.description: Zhaire Smith runs down the middle of the lane and throws down a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Smith gets up for one-handed flush

videos.description: Texas Tech's Jarrett Culver gets into the teeth of the defense and feeds Norense Odiase for a dunk.
videos.headline: Culver creates dunk with dribble penetration

videos.description: With 2.9 seconds on the clock, Justin Gray drills a deep 3-pointer before the buzzer.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Gray buries 3

videos.description: Niem Stevenson delivers a lob to Zhaire Smith in transition for a two-handed alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Smith rises for alley-oop

videos.description: Terry Maston hits a left-shoulder hook shot to give Baylor its first lead since the beginning of the second half.
videos.headline: Maston gives Baylor the lead late
